1
00:00:50,980 --> 00:00:56,220
=Go Back Lover=

2
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:00,490
=Go Back Lover=

3
00:01:03,490 --> 00:01:07,690
(Year 2018, Senior Year winter break)

4
00:01:21,580 --> 00:01:22,830
That was great.

5
00:01:24,580 --> 00:01:25,780
When did you get home?

6
00:01:25,860 --> 00:01:26,910
Xingyan.

7
00:01:27,350 --> 00:01:28,140
I just got back.

8
00:01:29,190 --> 00:01:30,020
Changhao.

9
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,300
What made you

10
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:32,580
suddenly come

11
00:01:32,580 --> 00:01:33,940
to get piano lessons from Xingruo?

12
00:01:34,190 --> 00:01:36,380
I'm about to take my piano exam.

13
00:01:36,470 --> 00:01:37,190
Aunt Pei said

14
00:01:37,190 --> 00:01:39,580
Xingruo is really good at the piano.

15
00:01:39,710 --> 00:01:41,110
So I came to ask Xingruo

16
00:01:41,110 --> 00:01:42,630
to give me some tips.

17
00:01:43,300 --> 00:01:43,910
I see.

18
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:44,990
You practice well, then.

19
00:01:45,110 --> 00:01:46,220
I'll leave you two be.

20
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:50,470
Come, let's go over it again.

21
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,140
Start.

22
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:12,380
Xingruo,

23
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:14,110
thank you for today.

24
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:15,270
You're welcome.

25
00:02:15,460 --> 00:02:17,460
If you want to practice some more
before the exam,

26
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:18,430
look for me again.

27
00:02:18,900 --> 00:02:19,550
Okay.

28
00:02:20,230 --> 00:02:21,020
Done practicing?

29
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:22,830
I got food delivery.

30
00:02:23,110 --> 00:02:24,140
Let's eat together.

31
00:02:24,140 --> 00:02:25,710
- Okay.
- Thanks, Xingyan.

32
00:02:25,940 --> 00:02:26,550
Let's go.

33
00:02:28,550 --> 00:02:29,340
Go on.

34
00:02:33,270 --> 00:02:36,580
How come you seem
especially happy today?

35
00:02:37,950 --> 00:02:38,580
Yeah,

36
00:02:38,830 --> 00:02:40,300
watching you teach him piano just now

37
00:02:41,270 --> 00:02:43,390
suddenly made me think of something.

38
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:44,460
What is it?

39
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:47,430
I thought that scene just now

40
00:02:47,510 --> 00:02:49,790
would be how our future family
would look.

41
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:51,990
Xingyan, Xingruo,

42
00:02:51,990 --> 00:02:53,710
come and eat, quick.

43
00:02:55,270 --> 00:02:55,900
Coming.

44
00:02:58,610 --> 00:03:04,890
=Episode 23=
(You defined how happiness looks.)

45
00:03:05,050 --> 00:03:08,090
(Love House)

46
00:03:23,230 --> 00:03:24,900
Since everyone is here,

47
00:03:25,110 --> 00:03:26,580
I'll keep it short.

48
00:03:26,790 --> 00:03:27,580
Just now,

49
00:03:28,020 --> 00:03:31,110
Mr. Zhang and I met with
the media platform's person-in-charge.

50
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:31,950
He said

51
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:35,060
that the public opinion this time
had a big effect

52
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:36,110
on our show.

53
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:37,620
So the show

54
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:39,230
will be suspended for rectification.

55
00:03:39,580 --> 00:03:42,550
When it will be resumed
is yet to be determined.

56
00:03:44,010 --> 00:03:44,860
I knew it.

57
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:46,060
So do we continue editing?

58
00:03:47,340 --> 00:03:49,830
What about the parts
that haven't been shot?

59
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:51,230
Those pending

60
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:52,790
will be put on hold for now.

61
00:03:52,990 --> 00:03:54,860
The reason we gathered everyone today

62
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:56,340
was to make this announcement.

63
00:03:56,620 --> 00:03:57,550
Rest assured.

64
00:03:57,740 --> 00:04:01,110
We will recompense you
according to the actual number of days.

65
00:04:06,270 --> 00:04:07,340
I met vlogger

66
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:08,430
who made the video.

67
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,430
He was indeed instructed to do so.

68
00:04:10,670 --> 00:04:12,110
And who instructed him?

69
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:13,860
That person

70
00:04:15,550 --> 00:04:16,950
is in our team.

71
00:04:20,510 --> 00:04:22,740
He's handed over all the details.

72
00:04:23,670 --> 00:04:25,350
All the chat logs are in here.

73
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:26,790
You can take a look.

74
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:32,990
Lu Xingyan, what are you doing?

75
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,260
I know.

76
00:04:37,030 --> 00:04:39,470
You've worked with these people
for many years.

77
00:04:39,550 --> 00:04:41,300
You feel bad for publicly
vilifying the culprit.

78
00:04:41,620 --> 00:04:43,230
So I'll do it for you.

79
00:04:45,740 --> 00:04:46,550
What are you doing?

80
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:48,620
I don't want to see it.

81
00:04:48,740 --> 00:04:50,500
I believe every one of them.

82
00:04:50,590 --> 00:04:52,060
Because they're members of my team.

83
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:54,260
We've been through so much.

84
00:04:54,820 --> 00:04:56,550
If someone had betrayed the team,

85
00:04:56,550 --> 00:04:58,550
I'm sure they had their reasons.

86
00:04:58,550 --> 00:04:59,430
Producer Shen.

87
00:04:59,790 --> 00:05:00,820
You need to face the music.

88
00:05:00,820 --> 00:05:02,500
Now is not the time to be sentimental.

89
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:03,940
I need you to wake up!

90
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:05,110
I'm wide awake.

91
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:07,060
If we read the chat logs,

92
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:08,700
there is no going back for us.

93
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:09,350
Then tell me,

94
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:11,260
what do we do
about the show getting suspended?

95
00:05:11,260 --> 00:05:13,030
When our hotel agreed to invest in you,

96
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:14,470
it is clearly stated in the contract.

97
00:05:14,470 --> 00:05:15,910
If the funding cannot be recovered,

98
00:05:15,910 --> 00:05:17,380
we will go after you for compensation.

99
00:05:17,380 --> 00:05:19,470
I will put my family home as collateral.

100
00:05:19,860 --> 00:05:20,990
I will deal with the money.

101
00:05:20,990 --> 00:05:22,110
I will bear the responsibility, okay?

102
00:05:22,110 --> 00:05:22,940
I don't care what you'll do.

103
00:05:22,940 --> 00:05:24,620
I'm going to get my lawyer
to deal with you all.

104
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:25,820
I wish you good luck.

105
00:05:41,030 --> 00:05:41,620
What's the matter?

106
00:05:49,620 --> 00:05:50,430
You did well.

107
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:54,500
Don't worry.

108
00:05:55,180 --> 00:05:56,700
I will get in touch
with the boss for you.

109
00:06:16,860 --> 00:06:17,500
Come in.

110
00:06:20,790 --> 00:06:21,380
Mr. Lu.

111
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:27,700
You asked for me, sir?

112
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:30,260
You should know

113
00:06:31,110 --> 00:06:33,260
that the platform has suspended
the show for rectification.

114
00:06:34,030 --> 00:06:35,940
We probably won't be getting back
our investment.

115
00:06:37,940 --> 00:06:39,740
Draft up an indemnification agreement

116
00:06:40,350 --> 00:06:41,470
and discuss it with Producer Shen.

117
00:06:42,910 --> 00:06:44,470
Are we really doing that, sir?

118
00:06:45,230 --> 00:06:47,430
Why don't we give Xingruo
a bit more time?

119
00:06:47,470 --> 00:06:49,590
Perhaps things will turn around.

120
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:51,110
I can wait.

121
00:06:51,740 --> 00:06:53,430
But can Sun Inn wait?

122
00:06:53,910 --> 00:06:55,150
Our bet agreement with Kangte

123
00:06:55,150 --> 00:06:56,380
is expiring very soon.

124
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:57,860
In the current situation,

125
00:06:58,700 --> 00:07:00,670
do you expect me
to risk the hotel by waiting?

126
00:07:04,470 --> 00:07:05,300
I understand.

127
00:07:05,910 --> 00:07:08,230
I will talk to Xingruo today.

128
00:07:08,910 --> 00:07:10,030
But I hope

129
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:11,110
you two

130
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:13,180
won't become awkward
because of this matter.

131
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:14,670
After all,

132
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:16,620
it wasn't easy

133
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:19,300
for you two to get back together.

134
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:21,030
After so long,

135
00:07:22,620 --> 00:07:24,550
she hasn't changed one bit.

136
00:07:26,030 --> 00:07:27,030
She is always,

137
00:07:27,740 --> 00:07:29,430
always thinking about herself.

138
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:31,180
Still as obstinate as ever.

139
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:33,890
I don't want to talk about it anymore.

140
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:36,110
Inform me once you've talked to her.

141
00:07:37,230 --> 00:07:38,030
Alright.

142
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:39,940
Don't be too upset.

143
00:07:40,230 --> 00:07:41,260
Have a good rest.

144
00:07:42,110 --> 00:07:43,150
I'm going to go.

145
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:47,500
Lawyer Zhai.

146
00:07:55,940 --> 00:07:56,860
It's been many years.

147
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:58,860
Thank you for all you've done.

148
00:08:00,820 --> 00:08:02,150
Why are you being so polite with me?

149
00:08:02,910 --> 00:08:03,550
I'm off.

150
00:08:42,300 --> 00:08:43,060
Xingruo.

151
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:48,670
I can't bear to walk another step today,

152
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:50,510
so I troubled you to come here instead.

153
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,340
It's fine.

154
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:55,430
The compensation for Sun Inn

155
00:08:55,430 --> 00:08:57,060
is part of my job scope.

156
00:08:57,270 --> 00:08:58,820
Anyway, I come to the hotel

157
00:08:58,820 --> 00:08:59,910
a few times a week.

158
00:09:00,180 --> 00:09:01,790
It's almost like my second home.

159
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:05,910
When I got here, I noticed

160
00:09:05,940 --> 00:09:07,060
that the cameras

161
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:08,220
have all been removed.

162
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:10,180
Did you really stop the recording?

163
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,460
I asked them all to go home.

164
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:14,460
Because...

165
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:16,220
we have to minimize the loss.

166
00:09:18,820 --> 00:09:19,670
Are you okay?

167
00:09:23,340 --> 00:09:24,870
I've been working so hard

168
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:28,060
and this is the result I get.

169
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:30,150
To be honest,

170
00:09:31,510 --> 00:09:33,220
I feel pretty bummed.

171
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:36,870
Is there anything I can help with?

172
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:41,150
It's already come to this.

173
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:43,630
What else can we do?

174
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:46,150
Just let it be.

175
00:09:47,220 --> 00:09:48,790
But actually,

176
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:50,180
there are a few things

177
00:09:50,180 --> 00:09:52,700
that I found odd
and couldn't figure out.

178
00:09:53,180 --> 00:09:56,220
Could you analyze it for me?

179
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:57,750
Tell me.

180
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:01,870
There's one thing
I can't wrap my head around.

181
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:03,550
During the shoot,

182
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,300
Huang Bing had sued us

183
00:10:05,300 --> 00:10:06,870
following Yang Tianjiao's instruction.

184
00:10:06,870 --> 00:10:07,870
You know it, right?

185
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:10,150
I heard about it after.

186
00:10:11,630 --> 00:10:14,940
Although I didn't have much interaction
with Yang Tianjiao,

187
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:16,150
I have a feeling

188
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:18,460
she isn't a very meticulous person.

189
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:20,980
But she clearly stated
the sum of compensation

190
00:10:21,390 --> 00:10:23,510
and even asked Shi Qin
to take me to court.

191
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:24,910
Now,

192
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:27,030
how did she think of that?

193
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:31,510
Listen, Xingruo.

194
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:33,980
This matter is already
water under the bridge.

195
00:10:34,060 --> 00:10:35,300
You should think about

196
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:36,790
what you should do right now instead.

197
00:10:37,790 --> 00:10:38,630
You're right.

198
00:10:38,980 --> 00:10:40,580
The incident with Li Qi

199
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:42,150
is also pretty weird.

200
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:43,430
I mean,

201
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:45,300
getting Li Qi to cause a scene

202
00:10:45,430 --> 00:10:48,060
meant getting him to Xingcheng
from the county.

203
00:10:48,270 --> 00:10:49,870
Also, on the day of the live stream,

204
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:51,580
he had to sneak past security
at the venue

205
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:52,790
to get to the streaming site.

206
00:10:52,790 --> 00:10:54,460
Plus, he had to have installed

207
00:10:54,460 --> 00:10:56,430
the other cameras
at the site beforehand.

208
00:10:56,550 --> 00:10:57,300
How could he

209
00:10:57,300 --> 00:10:59,030
do all of that by himself?

210
00:10:59,670 --> 00:11:00,940
Hence why I think

211
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:03,030
that the person who instructed him

212
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:04,910
must be very familiar

213
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,150
with the show.

214
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:16,550
Are you implying that...

215
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,430
there's a mole in your team?

216
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:23,580
Me and them are in the same boat.

217
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:26,030
Sink or swim, we're in it together.

218
00:11:26,180 --> 00:11:27,550
If the show gets cancelled,

219
00:11:27,550 --> 00:11:28,940
they wouldn't even get

220
00:11:28,940 --> 00:11:30,150
the most basic pay.

221
00:11:35,510 --> 00:11:36,820
I think...

222
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:38,430
Maybe you should go

223
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:41,180
and ask Shi Qin.

224
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:45,550
Did she look for Li Qi again?

225
00:11:46,390 --> 00:11:47,180
I'm guessing

226
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:49,460
there's a secret mastermind.

227
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:51,820
They utterly despise our show,

228
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:53,630
and so they found someone

229
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:55,390
on our team

230
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:58,980
and offered him something better
than the pay.

231
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:01,580
That's why he was willing
to take the risk

232
00:12:01,700 --> 00:12:03,390
and created this mess for us.

233
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:10,390
Xingruo, I think you need to let it go.

234
00:12:11,060 --> 00:12:13,220
Your analysis sound

235
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:14,580
pretty scary to me.

236
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:15,460
That's not it.

237
00:12:15,460 --> 00:12:16,550
Listen to me.

238
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:18,180
They had another trick up their sleeve.

239
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:20,460
The moment we released
the lawyer's letter,

240
00:12:20,820 --> 00:12:22,460
someone posted the video

241
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:24,150
taken at the alleyway.

242
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:26,150
Then a vlogger immediately
made an analysis video

243
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:28,670
and said we were sending
Li Qi death threats.

244
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:30,060
You tell me.

245
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:31,220
Could Li Qi

246
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:32,870
have come up with all that himself?

247
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:34,670
Here's the thing, Xingruo.

248
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:35,750
As an attorney,

249
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,270
I have to remind you.

250
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:39,270
Everything is based on evidence.

251
00:12:39,430 --> 00:12:41,910
I know you're trying
to save the show's reputation.

252
00:12:41,910 --> 00:12:44,390
But making baseless assumptions
won't get you anywhere.

253
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:45,670
What about

254
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:47,750
I help you get in touch
with that vlogger?

255
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:49,390
Find out exactly what's going on.

256
00:12:49,390 --> 00:12:51,430
We're old friends after all.

257
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:53,430
I really wish to help you out.

258
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:54,460
Don't worry.

259
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:57,180
Lu Xingyan has already
contacted the vlogger.

260
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,940
He even provided us with evidence.

261
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:00,820
In fact, after that,

262
00:13:01,060 --> 00:13:03,390
I wasn't going to pursue the matter.

263
00:13:04,220 --> 00:13:05,510
But to my surprise,

264
00:13:06,460 --> 00:13:07,300
that person

265
00:13:08,100 --> 00:13:10,030
came looking for me on their own.

266
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:19,940
I'm sorry.

267
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:23,700
I told the vlogger

268
00:13:23,870 --> 00:13:25,180
to make that video.

269
00:13:31,060 --> 00:13:31,750
He Ming.

270
00:13:33,510 --> 00:13:35,270
Finally, you chose
to come clean with me.

271
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:38,660
You...

272
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:41,910
You already knew?

273
00:13:42,150 --> 00:13:43,820
The chat logs in the USB drive.

274
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:45,910
I've seen it.

275
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:49,750
He Ming.

276
00:13:50,820 --> 00:13:52,870
I went over every person around me,

277
00:13:52,870 --> 00:13:54,180
but it never crossed my mind

278
00:13:54,180 --> 00:13:55,790
that the culprit would be you.

279
00:13:55,980 --> 00:13:57,870
Do you know what I was thinking

280
00:13:57,870 --> 00:13:59,300
when I read the chat logs yesterday?

281
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:01,060
That night,

282
00:14:01,940 --> 00:14:03,910
I kept reading the chat logs,

283
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:05,870
over and over again.

284
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:08,270
How I wish my eyes were deceiving me.

285
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,300
