567
00:30:32,630 --> 00:30:34,630
It was because he drove He Siyue's car.

568
00:30:35,940 --> 00:30:36,740
Yes.

569
00:30:38,430 --> 00:30:40,070
I gave him a chance.

570
00:30:41,220 --> 00:30:43,260
But he still wanted to leave me.

571
00:30:44,220 --> 00:30:46,020
So I had to punish him.

572
00:30:47,430 --> 00:30:48,220
Zhai Jiajing.

573
