581
00:31:16,310 --> 00:31:17,870
You won't be able to find anything.

582
00:31:20,630 --> 00:31:23,020
Inciting, guiding,

583
00:31:23,020 --> 00:31:25,630
those are not grounds
to constitute criminal action.

584
00:31:25,910 --> 00:31:27,740
Even if we bring this to court,

585
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:29,540
Li Qi and He Ming's testimonies

586
