can only be considered
as same case accusation.

587
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:34,830
You won't be able to prove anything.

588
00:31:35,830 --> 00:31:36,670
Shen Xingruo,

589
00:31:38,110 --> 00:31:40,630
no one can say for sure
if I'd be convicted.

590
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:43,540
