591
00:31:43,740 --> 00:31:45,980
And because of your rogue actions,

592
00:31:46,670 --> 00:31:48,260
Lu Xingyan has totally given up on you.

593
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:50,350
He asked me to come today

594
00:31:53,110 --> 00:31:55,830
because he wants to be recompensed
for your garbage of a show.

595
00:31:56,070 --> 00:31:56,980
Well?

596
00:31:58,630 --> 00:32:01,220
How does it feel
to have someone take away

597
00:32:02,670 --> 00:32:03,830
the most important thing to you?

598
00:32:07,070 --> 00:32:08,350
The most important thing to her

599
00:32:08,940 --> 00:32:10,260
is not something anyone can take away.

600
00:32:11,430 --> 00:32:12,740
Why are you here?

601
00:32:14,150 --> 00:32:15,390
If I hadn't come,

602
00:32:16,950 --> 00:32:18,740
I'd never have known
you were this kind of person.

603
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:20,670
No...

604
00:32:23,630 --> 00:32:24,700
Let me explain.

605
00:32:25,460 --> 00:32:26,830
I did all this

606
00:32:27,500 --> 00:32:29,540
because I like you.

607
00:32:31,020 --> 00:32:33,020
The stuff you said about high school?

608
00:32:33,830 --> 00:32:35,070
I've forgotten all of it.

609
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:38,740
At work, we're merely normal colleagues.

610
00:32:38,940 --> 00:32:40,630
I can tell you right now.

611
00:32:41,070 --> 00:32:42,150
In this world,

612
00:32:43,430 --> 00:32:44,740
there's only one person I can love.

613
00:32:46,500 --> 00:32:48,070
And that person
can only be Shen Xingruo.

614
00:32:51,260 --> 00:32:52,980
I did so much for you.

615
00:32:54,150 --> 00:32:55,500
How am I worse than her?

616
00:32:55,500 --> 00:32:57,830
Why couldn't you take notice of me?

617
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:04,780
Did you do it for me?

618
00:33:05,390 --> 00:33:07,830
Or was it to fulfill
your demented possessiveness?

619
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:11,740
To satisfy your own selfish interests,

620
00:33:12,330 --> 00:33:14,020
you put the entire
production team's efforts

621
00:33:14,020 --> 00:33:16,020
and the hotel's investment in danger.

622
00:33:21,540 --> 00:33:23,220
How many people suffered because of you?

623
00:33:24,150 --> 00:33:26,020
He Siyue almost lost his life!

624
00:33:31,110 --> 00:33:31,910
Zhai Jiajing.

625
00:33:34,700 --> 00:33:36,220
Stop making yourself look good.

626
00:33:38,070 --> 00:33:39,220
In your heart,

627
00:33:40,670 --> 00:33:41,630
there's only yourself.

628
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:57,630
Lu Xingyan.

629
00:34:00,150 --> 00:34:02,020
You've really disappointed me.

630
00:34:04,070 --> 00:34:06,350
I thought you were the clear-headed one.

631
00:34:07,260 --> 00:34:09,540
I thought you'd know
who's right and wrong.

632
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:12,150
And that you'd know who to choose.

633
00:34:18,220 --> 00:34:19,300
But it doesn't matter now.

634
00:34:20,910 --> 00:34:22,580
Shen Xingruo's show

635
00:34:23,620 --> 00:34:25,060
is completely ruined.

636
00:34:26,750 --> 00:34:30,060
Kangte Capital's bet agreement
is about to expire.

637
00:34:31,910 --> 00:34:34,140
If you two want to die together,

638
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:37,660
I can offer you my best wishes.

639
00:34:41,660 --> 00:34:43,580
If you hadn't just said those things,

640
00:34:45,060 --> 00:34:46,940
my show would've really been done for.

641
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:50,020
But,

642
00:34:53,790 --> 00:34:54,540
I'm very thankful

643
00:34:54,540 --> 00:34:56,390
that you clarified things on my behalf.

644
00:35:10,430 --> 00:35:11,350
What do you mean?

645
00:35:13,020 --> 00:35:14,060
In this world,

646
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:16,270
you're not the only lawyer.

647
00:35:17,870 --> 00:35:20,460
Qin had long guessed your intention

648
00:35:21,020 --> 00:35:22,750
to avoid legal issues.

649
00:35:24,020 --> 00:35:25,710
It's no use even if we have

650
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:28,140
Li Qi and He Ming's testimonies.

651
00:35:28,500 --> 00:35:29,830
Because their testimonies

652
00:35:29,830 --> 00:35:32,020
can only be regarded as evidence
of the same case.

653
00:35:32,020 --> 00:35:34,660
We need to find more direct proof.

654
00:35:35,830 --> 00:35:37,060
What should we do then?

655
00:35:38,540 --> 00:35:39,580
I have an idea.

656
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:48,540
Evidence for the same case
couldn't trip you up.

657
00:35:48,830 --> 00:35:50,750
Then we'd get you on video

658
00:35:51,430 --> 00:35:53,230
testifying your crimes.

659
00:35:54,460 --> 00:35:55,500
As it is now,

660
00:35:56,830 --> 00:35:57,830
there should be

661
00:35:58,790 --> 00:35:59,940
enough evidence.

662
00:36:00,500 --> 00:36:01,710
We've called the police.

663
00:36:02,310 --> 00:36:04,270
We'll hand these over to the police.

664
00:36:05,350 --> 00:36:06,830
Anything else you want to say?

665
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:10,270
So...

666
00:36:12,620 --> 00:36:13,830
the whole time,

667
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:19,540
you all put on a show to trick me.

668
00:36:21,710 --> 00:36:23,310
If I hadn't made you believe

669
00:36:23,310 --> 00:36:24,660
that you had won,

670
00:36:25,830 --> 00:36:28,460
would you have willingly
told me the truth?

671
00:36:31,140 --> 00:36:32,540
I hope you didn't think

672
00:36:32,540 --> 00:36:33,660
that your plan was foolproof.

673
00:36:34,750 --> 00:36:37,100
Or that you outsmarted everyone else.

674
00:36:38,430 --> 00:36:40,830
Your possessiveness
has driven you crazy.

675
00:36:42,580 --> 00:36:44,020
To get what you desired,

676
00:36:44,020 --> 00:36:46,460
you dreamt up unrealistic illusions.

677
00:36:47,230 --> 00:36:50,020
Zhai Jiajing, it's time to face reality.

678
00:36:50,500 --> 00:36:52,020
The things and people you wanted

679
00:36:52,020 --> 00:36:53,430
never belonged to you.

680
00:36:53,430 --> 00:36:54,830
Shut up!

681
00:37:04,140 --> 00:37:05,020
Get the security!

682
00:37:25,710 --> 00:37:27,910
You really gave me a heart attack.

683
00:37:27,910 --> 00:37:29,140
She had a knife,

684
00:37:29,140 --> 00:37:30,500
but you just rushed forward.

685
00:37:31,230 --> 00:37:32,710
I'd say you shocked me.

686
00:37:32,830 --> 00:37:34,870
Before I knew it,
you had pinned her on the floor.

687
00:37:37,910 --> 00:37:39,100
When did you learn that move?

688
00:37:40,020 --> 00:37:42,310
I had guessed
there would be a confrontation.

689
00:37:42,310 --> 00:37:44,100
So I learned a few tricks from Chen Zhu.

690
00:37:44,140 --> 00:37:44,710
Well?

691
00:37:44,710 --> 00:37:46,020
Was I not super cool?

692
00:37:46,940 --> 00:37:48,540
About as cool as me.

693
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:50,350
I thought

694
00:37:50,350 --> 00:37:52,790
I could finally get a scene
of the knight saving the beauty.

695
00:37:55,710 --> 00:37:57,750
This time, I managed to save the show

696
00:37:58,140 --> 00:37:59,230
and you.

697
00:37:59,690 --> 00:38:01,500
Doesn't that count as the knight
saving the beauty?

698
00:38:04,270 --> 00:38:04,910
Sure,

699
00:38:05,620 --> 00:38:06,430
it counts.

700
00:38:09,910 --> 00:38:10,940
The second time.

