for the last episode?)

714
00:38:41,890 --> 00:38:44,250
I prepared a surprise for Lu Xingyan.

715
00:38:44,970 --> 00:38:46,690
Could you tell us what it is?

716
00:38:49,770 --> 00:38:50,930
It's something

717
00:38:51,250 --> 00:38:53,250
